When the Create or Comment email handler is used, the notification can be captured and distributed using the Issue Updated listener; however, adding a group to that listener can cause a lot of unnecessary spam. We'd prefer to have these comments trigger an Issue Commented listener, to allow notifications to be more finely configured.

