To be more intuitive there are two changes suggestion on *Global Permission* page:

- The groups displayed on Global Permission need to show the *Group (group_name)* as in project permission, it helps the customer to not get confused if it’s an username or a group.


- The *View Users* link make an impression that it will redirect to the list of user on that group and not to all available users on instance.
